This paper involves training deep reinforcement learning agents in a 3D virtual environment, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of interactive machine learning (IML) and human teachers also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the importance of visual features and aliasing, indicating a potential focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR).
